<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c5">ح ن ذ:</span> <span class="c2">(حَنَذَ)</span> الشَّاةَ شَوَاهَا وَجَعَلَ فَوْقَهَا حِجَارَةً مُحْمَاةً لِتُنْضِجَهَا فَهِيَ <span class="c2">(حَنِيذٌ)</span> وَبَابُهُ ضَرَبَ.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>